    "Therefore, we focused on comparing the number of men and women.",
    "The difference was not statistically significant (odds ratio = 5.5, p = 0.1032) which might be attributed to the small sample size.",
    "People with dementia identified as European (14) and Asian (1).",
    "Their highest degrees were vocational training/trade certificate (2 respondents), secondary education/high school (9), Bachelor's degree or equivalent (1), or Postgraduate degree (3).",
